snippet.title: Turning Point USA
snippet.description:
Check here for the latest videos from Turning Point USA.

Turning Point USA is an American 501(c)3 non-profit charitable organization whose mission is to identify, educate, train, and organize students to promote freedom.

Here, you'll find shows such as Freedom Fights for daily content, POPlitics on weekdays, Real America on Thursdays, and Benny on the Block on Fridays.

We believe in Free Markets, Limited Government, and Fiscal Responsibility.
